HEADWORD: Curriculum
<hw>Cur*ric"u*lum</hw> <pr>(k?r-r?k"?-l?m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> E. <plw>Curriculums</plw> (-l<?/mz), L.
